Payment from abroad:
For orders from abroad, we expect payment by an accepted credit card.
If the credit card is not accepted, you must pay in advance.

Payment from within the country:

If you are already a customer of Software Direct KG, you can only pay using the convenient direct debit procedure.

If you are a new customer:

For invoice amounts up to €25, you must pay via the chargeable Online Payment System. To do this, dial the telephone number 0190123467 and follow the instructions.

For amounts over €25, we expect payment by an accepted credit card. If the credit card is not accepted, you must pay in advance.

Accepted credit card:
We check whether the credit card is accepted by the clearinghouse Clearsoft.
